                    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d14685.694477333973!2d72.5702377!3d23.044926!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xbcf52d4d59c75b70!2sSeyom%20Business%20Solutions!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1669718220300!5m2!1sen!2sin"
